videos.description: Brea Beal drives to the rim and draws the contact, sending Myah Taylor to the floor, then banks in the layup to put South Carolina up ten on Mississippi State.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Beal plays ‘bully ball’ for and-1) 2020/03/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Beal plays 'bully ball' for and-1

videos.description: Tyasha Harris runs the fast break and dishes it to Destanni Henderson, who lays it in to force a Mississippi State timeout.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Gamecocks double the lead on fast-break layup) 2020/03/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gamecocks double the lead on fast-break layup

videos.description: South Carolina's Mikiah Herbert Harrigan and Mississippi State's Yemiyah Morris both receive technical fouls for jawing at each other following a fight for a loose ball.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Tempers flare in SEC championship game) 2020/03/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tempers flare in SEC championship game

videos.description: South Carolina's Mikiah Herbert Harrigan chases down Jordan Danberry and swats her shot into the seats, then celebrates with a flex for the crowd.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Herbert Harrigan swats shot and flexes to celebrate) 2020/03/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Herbert Harrigan swats shot and flexes to celebrate

videos.description: South Carolina demonstrates beautiful ball movement, working the ball up the court on four passes and just one dribble, resulting in a Brea Beal layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Pretty passing leads to South Carolina layup) 2020/03/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pretty passing leads to South Carolina layup
